{"tid":1911651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俾我地早十年既消費者運動先驅龐一鳴：要用同樣力度支持本地生產","createTime":"2020-03-05T13:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T17:34:02.000Z","uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1bb0bae6313b26f76e75b129fc09b80b8a88bf","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/AYDZ6ZHLEI4MB7LQMIVCFXZRGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FAYDZ6ZHLEI4MB7LQMIVCFXZRGQ%2F&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=01eb06e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FAYDZ6ZHLEI4MB7LQMIVCFXZRGQ%2F&h=1c2fefc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/AYDZ6ZHLEI4MB7LQMIVCFXZRGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n^自己㩒入去先！俾蘋果賺click rate!<br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n<br />\n十年前，龐一鳴推動消費者抗爭，杯葛地產霸權，被不少人笑脫離現實。十年後的今天，形勢大逆轉，不少人將抗爭融入消費；光顧「黃店」，是每天指定動作。<br />\n<br />\n對於大家對黃色經濟圈的投入度，龐一鳴形容是「夠傻」，但要壯大黃圈，這位香港消費者運動先鋒認為大家尚有不足。<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n龐一鳴形容，當年（2010）這班認為抗爭無用的人，是一班「已經認輸嘅人」。然而，經歷過雨傘運動、反送中運動，十年後的今天，社會氣氛大大改變，越來越多香港人發現自己也是被欺壓的一群，於是覺醒，「要一步登天係冇可能，全部嘢都係揼石仔咁出嚟」，不再如以往般質疑行動有沒有用，反而「做得幾多得幾多」，「黃色經濟圈」的運動因而誕生&mdash;&mdash;大家矢志於日常消費中抗爭。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n龐一鳴當然支持黃色經濟圈，但認為現時行動較局限於「消費圈」，忽略「本地生產」。「而家係一個黃色『消費圈』多啲，特別係消費飲食業層面，遠遠未有任何經濟規模，因為當中完全冇本地生產。」<br />\n缺乏本地生產，市民安危亦會受影響。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n「即係話我哋嘅日用品，全部係外地生產，都係一啲大集團嘅資金、紅色資本、藍色資本去擁有，其實冇一個黃色經濟圈誕生。所以，一定要由源頭，着手創造、生產我哋需要。」如何做？「所謂本地生產，唔一定喺香港實體土地。」龐一鳴大膽建議，由香港人發動，在外地設廠，專門供應香港。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n龐一鳴卻認為，批評者不應只停留於投訴「黃店」產品來自內地，反而該「行前多步」，向商家介紹其他來源的貨品，促使黃店「良性改良」。"},{"pid":"9fe5c99bc6365ec7855ddba187874f215def3798","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"真先驅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都係跟大隊行既時候佢已經眾人皆醉我獨醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224ed1b43d5b9e491a2fe10b0dca5a0b7d1e6379","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104878537b4a5aaac45e940485f8695acb1b6063","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"71ac0dbaf873b0509173f09370477b8b71b0bc5b","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e6fdfd8164ffa3610641d7e3a228a6bf6ed8a1","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a2e54d7ae83facfd712e452132c71cf7041b45","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77589cc14064479eba5c4314507a3e4120ea3e9a","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"推到本地生產成為黃色經濟圈既下一步!!"},{"pid":"7d39bd52f6554d15c6d569d10c4e62c97f9bb31a","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9b0c0e3faf99676bd198ae02dc10e03afb65cb","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6240ea35f104dfd488b8050f43878ac8c70624fb","tid":1911651,"uid":350943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.